HE GETS PUT
ON THE NATIONAL TEAM,

00:03:56.802 --> 00:03:59.338
AND THE NATIONAL TEAM
TAKE HIM DOWN

00:03:59.371 --> 00:04:00.940
TO THE PAN AMERICAN GAMES,

00:04:00.973 --> 00:04:03.175
AND THE BIGGEST SUPERPOWER

00:04:03.208 --> 00:04:07.713
IN THE PAN AMERICAN GAMES
IS CUBA,

00:04:07.746 --> 00:04:10.850
FIDEL CASTRO'S CUBA,

00:04:10.883 --> 00:04:15.454
BECAUSE FIDEL LOVES COMMUNISM

00:04:15.487 --> 00:04:17.323
AND HE LOVES BASEBALL.

00:04:17.356 --> 00:04:19.325
THOSE ARE A COUPLE THINGS
HE LOVES.

00:04:19.358 --> 00:04:21.694
THERE IS
A HUGE SEPARATION

00:04:21.727 --> 00:04:25.464
BETWEEN THE AMERICAN
AND CUBAN REGIME.

00:04:25.497 --> 00:04:29.368
JIM ABBOTT WALKS OUT
AND STARTS FOR AMERICA,

00:04:29.401 --> 00:04:33.172
AND EVERYBODY IN THE PLACE
IS LIKE, BOO!

00:04:33.205 --> 00:04:34.674
WE ARE CUBAN,

00:04:34.707 --> 00:04:36.809
THE GREATEST BASEBALL PLAYERS
IN THE WORLD.

00:04:36.842 --> 00:04:40.146
HOW CAN YOU POSSIBLY THINK
YOU CAN BEAT US?

00:04:40.179 --> 00:04:43.182
AMERICANS WITH TWO HANDS
CAN'T BEAT US.

00:04:43.215 --> 00:04:46.185
