IN THE STAND,

00:05:20.819 --> 00:05:22.455
BECAUSE THEY WERE NOT
ALLOWED IN CUBA.

00:05:22.488 --> 00:05:26.559
AND, LIKE, FIDEL CASTRO
CAME DOWN,

00:05:26.592 --> 00:05:30.496
SHOOK HIS HAND
AND WAS LIKE, NICE.

00:05:30.529 --> 00:05:32.531
THAT WAS A BIG DEAL,

00:05:32.564 --> 00:05:34.934
TELLING
AN AMERICAN PLAYER "NICE."

00:05:34.967 --> 00:05:37.703
AND HE WENT ON TO PLAY
FOR, LIKE, TEN YEARS

00:05:37.736 --> 00:05:39.939
IN THE MAJOR LEAGUES.

00:05:39.972 --> 00:05:42.341
EVERY STEP OF THE WAY,

00:05:42.374 --> 00:05:45.411
HIGH SCHOOL, COLLEGE,
THE MAJORS,

00:05:45.444 --> 00:05:47.246
PEOPLE SAID,
CAN YOU DO IT?

00:05:47.279 --> 00:05:49.648
HE WAS SUCH A POSITIVE PERSON.

00:05:49.681 --> 00:05:52.885
HE WOULD SAY STUFF LIKE,
EVERYONE HAS DISABILITIES.

00:05:52.918 --> 00:05:56.155
MINE ARE JUST MORE VISIBLE.

00:05:56.188 --> 00:05:59.258
IT MAKES EVERYBODY FEEL

00:05:59.291 --> 00:06:00.359
THAT THEY'RE IN HIS CAMP.

00:06:00.392 --> 00:06:04.897
IT'S INCREDIBLE.
